=== Test 1: Explicit column_names_to_sum with nested Tuple ===
Explicit nested col - with FINAL:
1	(50,(70,90))	(100,200)	1000
2	(13,(15,17))	(50,60)	500
Explicit nested col - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(50,(70,90))	(100,200)	1000
2	(13,(15,17))	(50,60)	500
=== Test 2: Tuple in partition key ===
Tuple partition key - with FINAL:
1	(1,2)	(400,600)
Tuple partition key - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(1,2)	(400,600)
=== Test 3: Tuple sub-columns as partition and sorting keys ===
Tuple sub-col keys - with FINAL:
(1,10)	(400,600)
Tuple sub-col keys - after OPTIMIZE:
(1,10)	(400,600)
=== Test 4: Prefix search must not falsely skip flattened sub-columns ===
Prefix no false skip - with FINAL:
1	(300,120)	10
Prefix no false skip - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(300,120)	10
